      <title>惠誉在出售收益不佳后下调丹格特工业的评级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/fitch-downgrades-dangote-industries-after-soft-sale-proceeds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[惠誉评级下调了对丹格特工业有限公司信用度的评估，理由包括“该集团的流动性状况因处置收益低于预期而严重恶化”，并将其评级列入负面观察名单。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/fitch-downgrades-dangote-industries-after-soft-sale-proceeds</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 09:39:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛称在标普 500 指数下跌 5% 后买入通常可获利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/goldman-says-buying-s-p-500-after-5-drop-is-usually-profitable</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团对四十年数据的分析显示，在过去一个月出现如此大规模的暴跌之后买入美国股票通常都是有利可图的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/goldman-says-buying-s-p-500-after-5-drop-is-usually-profitable</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 09:37:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
